article.description: — Pierre Crockrell II had a career-high 21 points as Pacific topped San Diego 77-67 on Tuesday.
article.headline: Crockrell leads Pacific over San Diego 77-67
article.linkText: Crockrell leads Pacific over San Diego 77-67
article.story: SAN DIEGO -- — Pierre Crockrell II had a career-high 21 points as Pacific topped San Diego 77-67 on Tuesday. Crockrell made 9 of 12 shots. Broc Finstuen had 15 points for Pacific (8-7, 5-6 West Coast Conference). Jordan Bell added 13 points and eight rebounds, and Jeremiah Bailey had 12 points and seven rebounds. Joey Calcaterra had 12 points for the Toreros (3-9, 2-6). Yauhen Massalski added 11 points, 11 rebounds and five blocks. Josh Parrish also had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
